<li><a href="http://www.boston.com/ae/books/articles/2006/02/08/undermining_poor_nations_in_the_name_of_profit/" class="external text" title="http://www.boston.com/ae/books/articles/2006/02/08/undermining_poor_nations_in_the_name_of_profit/" rel="nofollow">Undermining poor nations in the name of profit</a>, The Boston Globe, February 08, 2006, by Michael Langan</li>
<li>A miss not a hit, Sunday Times (London), March 5, 2006, David Charters</li>
